    </div>
    <div class="neycher-stats__right">
      <div class="neycher-stats__grid">
        <div class="neycher-stats__item">
          <div class="neycher-stats__number-row">
            <span class="neycher-stats__number">94%</span>
            <svg class="neycher-stats__ring" width="36" height="36" viewBox="0 0 36 36">
              <circle cx="18" cy="18" r="15" fill="none" stroke="#e0e0e8" stroke-width="3"/>
              <circle cx="18" cy="18" r="15" fill="none" stroke="#8b8fc7" stroke-width="3" stroke-dasharray="88.5 94.2" stroke-dashoffset="23.6" stroke-linecap="round" transform="rotate(-90 18 18)"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <p class="neycher-stats__desc">Experienced a noticeable improvement in vaginal dryness</p>
        </div>
        <div class="neycher-stats__item">
          <div class="neycher-stats__number-row">
            <span class="neycher-stats__number">96%</span>
            <svg class="neycher-stats__ring" width="36" height="36" viewBox="0 0 36 36">
              <circle cx="18" cy="18" r="15" fill="none" stroke="#e0e0e8" stroke-width="3"/>
              <circle cx="18" cy="18" r="15" fill="none" stroke="#8b8fc7" stroke-width="3" stroke-dasharray="90.5 94.2" stroke-dashoffset="23.6" stroke-linecap="round" transform="rotate(-90 18 18)"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <p class="neycher-stats__desc">Reported positive impacts on other aspects of their life, such as emotional well-being</p>
        </div>
        <div class="neycher-stats__item">
          <div class="neycher-stats__number-row">
            <span class="neycher-stats__number">84%</span>
            <svg class="neycher-stats__ring" width="36" height="36" viewBox="0 0 36 36">
              <circle cx="18" cy="18" r="15" fill="none" stroke="#e0e0e8" stroke-width="3"/>
              <circle cx="18" cy="18" r="15" fill="none" stroke="#8b8fc7" stroke-width="3" stroke-dasharray="79.2 94.2" stroke-dashoffset="23.6" stroke-linecap="round" transform="rotate(-90 18 18)"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <p class="neycher-stats__desc">Stopped feeling pain during sex</p>
        </div>
        <div class="neycher-stats__item">
          <div class="neycher-stats__number-row">
            <span class="neycher-stats__number">88%</span>
            <svg class="neycher-stats__ring" width="36" height="36" viewBox="0 0 36 36">
              <circle cx="18" cy="18" r="15" fill="none" stroke="#e0e0e8" stroke-width="3"/>
              <circle cx="18" cy="18" r="15" fill="none" stroke="#8b8fc7" stroke-width="3" stroke-dasharray="82.9 94.2" stroke-dashoffset="23.6" stroke-linecap="round" transform="rotate(-90 18 18)"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <p class="neycher-stats__desc">Noticed improvements in their sexual relationships</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p class="neycher-stats__footnote">*Based on a 4-week study of woman ages 29-74 experiencing common vulvovaginal symptoms and general discomfort.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

{% stylesheet %}
.neycher-stats {
  padding: 80px 60px;
  max-width: 1440px;
  margin: 0 auto;
}
.neycher-stats__inner {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr 1.2fr;
  gap: 80px;
  align-items: start;
}
.neycher-stats__heading {
  margin-bottom: 28px;
}
.neycher-stats__heading em {
  font-style: italic;
}
.neycher-stats__text {
  font-family: var(--n-font);
  font-size: 15px;
  font-weight: 400;
  color: var(--n-color-body);
  line-height: 1.6;
  margin: 0;
  max-width: 480px;
}
.neycher-stats__grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
  gap: 48px 60px;
}
.neycher-stats__number-row {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 10px;
  margin-bottom: 10px;
}
.neycher-stats__number {
  font-family: var(--n-font);
  font-size: 56px;
  font-weight: 400;
  color: var(--n-color-heading);
  line-height: 1;
}
.neycher-stats__ring {
  flex-shrink: 0;
}
.neycher-stats__desc {
  font-family: var(--n-font);
  font-size: 14px;
  font-weight: 400;
  color: var(--n-color-body);
  margin: 0;
  line-height: 1.5;
}
.neycher-stats__footnote {
  font-family: var(--n-font);
  font-size: 12px;
  color: var(--n-color-muted);
  margin: 48px 0 0;
  line-height: 1.4;
}
@media screen and (max-width: 999px) {
  .neycher-stats__inner {
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 40px;
  }
}
@media screen and (max-width: 749px) {
  .neycher-stats {
    padding: 48px 16px;
  }
  .neycher-stats__grid {
    gap: 32px 24px;
  }
  .neycher-stats__number {
    font-size: 40px;
  }
}
{% endstylesheet %}

{% schema %}
{
  "name": "Neycher Stats",
  "class": "section-wrapper",
  "disabled_on": {
    "groups": ["header", "footer"]
  },
  "settings": [],
  "presets": [
    {
      "name": "Neycher Stats"
    }
  ]
}
{% endschema %}
